calc_variations:{tier:4,cat:'math',label:'Calculus of Variations',
desc:'Euler-Lagrange equations, functionals on function spaces, Hamiltonian mechanics, Noether\'s theorem (symmetry → conservation law), Hamilton-Jacobi theory, isoperimetric problems. The mathematical seed of optimal control.',
