os_systems:{tier:4,cat:'hw',label:'OS & Systems Programming',
desc:'Processes, virtual memory (paging, TLBs, page replacement), filesystems, I/O, scheduling algorithms, concurrency primitives (mutexes, semaphores, monitors, RCU), networking stack, kernel architecture. The software side of hardware.',
