functional_analysis:{tier:5,cat:'math',label:'Functional Analysis',
desc:'Banach and Hilbert spaces, bounded linear operators, spectral theorem (compact operators), Hahn-Banach theorem, open mapping, closed graph, distributions (Schwartz), Sobolev spaces, C*-algebras.',
