  {t:'Information Theory, Inference, and Learning Algorithms',a:'David MacKay',n:'Free online. Brilliant and broad.',},
  {t:'Probability Theory: The Logic of Science',a:'E. T. Jaynes',n:'Bayesian probability as extended logic. Important.',},
],lec:[
